# NAVIGATION FLOW (from Figma Prototype)

## Start: Landing Page

Landing
  - CTA "Explore resources" → Dashboard
  - CTA "Publish resource" → Login

Login
  - Success → Dashboard
  - Error → Stay + show error message

Dashboard
  - Click Resource Card → Resource Detail
  - + Publish Resource → Publish Page

Publish Page
  - Publish success → Resource Detail
  - Validation error → Stay on page

Resource Detail
  - Click Validate → Validation action
  - Click Reuse → Reuse flow

Profile
  - Click Resource → Resource Detail
